{"tid":2446404,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE提前解散 成員淚崩：我們也沒想到","createTime":"2021-03-14T12:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T08:33:20.000Z","uid":365024,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fec2d7e17df8ba7236bf2efa5910304bd5c83c51","tid":2446404,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:04:05.000Z","msg":"11日韓媒爆料，女團IZ*ONE確定於4月解散，並於昨（13）、今兩日開演唱會與粉絲告別，原先粉絲以為演唱會之後還會有解散專輯或其他行程，但成員在線上演唱會公布解散訊息，讓粉絲相當不捨。<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE為韓、日的限定女團，雖然粉絲知道合約到了遲早會解散，不料，在今（14）日的付費線上演唱會上直接宣布解散，仍令粉絲哀鴻遍野，無法接受這樣的解散方式，舞台上的成員與線上的粉絲全都哭成一片。<br />\n<br />\n唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3466635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3466635&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=99369a45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3466635&h=66035d69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3466635</a>"},{"pid":"3906f1b4b61b4ff354d7e082b38f39d1d7528502","tid":2446404,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61f680db8e4cd5e20b68b91c4947f11e087937f","tid":2446404,"uid":68678,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:06:52.000Z","msg":"咁都提前？"},{"pid":"6d3bea6fa42d187a2bd3e369c9e40032e63e9196","tid":2446404,"uid":190258,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e61f680db8e4cd5e20b68b91c4947f11e087937f","tid":2446404,"uid":68678,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"re